title: Trade Deadline Fallout
description:
Laura, Key, Marcus, and Adam react to Dan Snyder hiring the the Bank of America Securities to explore the sale of their franchise as well as the biggest trades that happed at the deadline. Who are the biggest winners and losers after the deadline? Why the Vikings have established themselves as a contender in the NFC.
